%% Real-time agent state event flow
%% ACD/DFO event -> StateAggregator (DynamoDB) -> Verint
%% Parallel path: StateCollector -> StatePublisher -> IEX
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant ACD as ACD / DFO
    participant KO as Kinesis<br/>Orch Stream
    participant SC as StateCollector<br/>(C#)
    participant KW as Kinesis<br/>WFM State
    participant SP as StatePublisher<br/>(C#)
    participant IEX as IEX (ASCWS)
    participant STC as StreamConsumer<br/>(Java)
    participant R as Redis<br/>(Redisson)
    participant Q as SQS SA queue
    participant SA as StateAggregator<br/>(Java)
    participant D as DynamoDB
    participant VP as VerintPublisher<br/>(Java, scheduled)
    participant V as Verint WFM

    ACD->>KO: orchestration event
    par C# transform path
        KO->>SC: KCL read shard record
        SC->>SC: OrchestrationParser.parse()
        SC->>SC: OrchestrationEventProcessor.transform()
        SC->>KW: publish WFM-centric event
        KW->>SP: KCL read
        SP->>IEX: POST /ascws (agent state)
    and Java aggregation path
        KO->>STC: KCL read shard record
        STC->>STC: route to RecordProcessor by event type
        STC->>R: write event (Redisson cluster)
        STC->>Q: send SQS notification
        Q->>SA: JMS deliver
        SA->>R: fetch event (MASTER_SLAVE client)
        SA->>SA: route to *AggregatorService
        SA->>D: PutItem (DynamoInserter)
    end

    Note over VP: Scheduled (cron)
    VP->>D: Query aggregated rows
    VP->>V: POST queue + agent reports
